Adding GPM KPI 19


GPM


1. Copy and paste the ‘Total Active Customers’ KPI card.
2. Uncheck the ‘Total Active Customers’ and select or drag the ‘GPM’ measure to the Fields section
3. Make the following changes:
General:
Height=114
Width=216
Position =>
Horizontal=1
Vertical=512
Title=On, Text= GPM
Font=Segoe UI (12)
Text color=#FFFFFF
Background color=#094780
Horizontal alignment=Center
Effects =>
Background=On
Background color=#F1F7F6
Transparency=0%
Visual boarder=on
Visual:
Callout Value =>
Font=Segoe UI Semibold (40)
Font color=#369191
Category label=Off
